            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, combine your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>horseradish</strong>, <strong>cider vinegar </strong>and<strong> sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a bowl</p><p>Add 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and<strong> </strong>a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>white BBQ sauce</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1595941921484-x200.jpg",
