            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken skin is crispy, reduce the heat to medium-high and turn the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> and cook for 8 min on the other side until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>smoky Alabama-style chicken</strong></p><p>While the chicken is cooking, wash and chop your <strong>lettuce </strong>into 2 wedges per person, then pat them dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut the <strong>smoky Alabama-style chicken</strong> in half on a clean chopping board</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
