          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1595941939237-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky Alabama-style chicken</strong> with the <strong>potato</strong> <strong>wedges</strong>,<strong> corn </strong>and<strong> lettuce wedges </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>white BBQ sauce</strong> over the chicken and lettuce wedges and garnish with the <strong>chopped chives</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
